  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice — factual stub. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">A pair of personal audio tools living at their own subdomains. <strong class=\"\">radio.ejfox</strong> is a one-button personal radio station — an always-on, \"ON AIR\" stream of shuffled music in the Vulpes aesthetic. <strong class=\"\">music.tools</strong> is the companion library for browsing and managing the catalog behind it.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"radio.ejfox — a personal &#x22;on air&#x22; radio station\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/ejfox-stations/radio.png\" alt=\"radio.ejfox — a personal &#x22;on air&#x22; radio station\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/ejfox-stations/radio.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/ejfox-stations/radio.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/ejfox-stations/radio.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/ejfox-stations/radio.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"radio.ejfox — a personal &#x22;on air&#x22; radio station\" width=\"1440\" height=\"813\" style=\"--splay-rot:-1.84deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1440×813\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-video w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">radio.ejfox — a personal \"on air\" radio station</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"music.tools — browsing the catalog\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/ejfox-stations/music.png\" alt=\"music.tools — browsing the catalog\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/ejfox-stations/music.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/ejfox-stations/music.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/ejfox-stations/music.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/ejfox-stations/music.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"music.tools — browsing the catalog\" width=\"1440\" height=\"4574\" style=\"--splay-rot:1.49deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1440×4574\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">music.tools — browsing the catalog</figcaption>\n</figure>",
